Description: Condition: This Jackson DK2 lefty is in excellent condition, with very little signs of wear. The Pro Series Dinky DK2 LH features an alder body, a 1-piece maple neck with graphite reinforcement, a 12"-16" compound radius, and an ebony fretboard. It's stacked with a Seymour Duncan Nazgul and Sentient humbuckers, and is equipped with a Jackson HT7 7-String hardtail bridge with a strings-thru-body design.
